    dc:description "Figure 9. Amara (Curtonotus) hiogoensis A dorsal habitus, female (Jiaohe, Jilin) B pronotum posterior angle (Jiaohe, Jilin) C male mesotibia (Jiaohe, Jilin) D lateral view of aedeagus (Jiaohe, Jilin) E right paramere (Jiaohe, Jilin) F apical lamella (Jiaohe, Jilin) G female gonocoxite. Scale bars: 5 mm (A); 1 mm (B-E); 0.5 mm (F, G)." ;
